ting%20the%20game%20themselves%20to%20avoid%20this.%20As%20such%2C%20any%20would-be%20Chen-Mao%20players%20must%20be%20player%201%20and%20manage%20resetting%20the%20game%20when%20necessary.%20%0A-%20To%20be%20player%201%20on%20Fightcade%2C%20you%20must%20be%20the%20one%20to%20challenge%20your%20opponent.%0A-%20Any%20desyncs%20caused%20by%20Chen-Mao%20will%20grant%20the%20game%20to%20their%20opponent.%0A-%20If%20a%20player%20forgets%20to%20reset%20the%20game%20upon%20a%20loss%20and%20picks%20Chen-Mao%20for%20the%20next%20match%2C%20the%20game%20must%20be%20reset%20before%20the%20match%20starts%20%28FIGHT%21%20appears%20on%20screen%29.%20Resetting%20the%20emulator%20once%20the%20match%20has%20started%20will%20grant%20the%20game%20to%20the%20Chen-Mao%20player%27s%20opponent.%0A%0A-%20These%20rules%20do%20not%20apply%20in%20case%20of%20a%20Chen-Mao%20mirror.%0A%0ANanami%20is%20banned%20to%20avoid%20desyncs.&prefill_Rules-Glitches=Any%20glitches%20that%20can%20cause%20the%20match%20to%20be%20completely%20unplayable%20%28e.g.%20by%20causing%20a%20softlock%20or%20a%20game%20freeze%29%20are%20banned.%20A%20player%20who%20triggers%20such%20a%20glitch%20has%20to%20forfeit%20the%20current%20game.&prefill_Rules-Chara%20Change=Winner%20must%20keep%20character.%20Loser%20may%20switch.&prefill_Rules-Game%20Settings=&prefill_Finals-Games%20per%20Set=3%2F5%20Games%20for%20Grand%20Finals%2C%203%2F5%20Games%20for%20Winners%20Finals%2C%203%2F5%20Games%20for%20Losers%20Finals&prefill_Pools-Games%20per%20Set=2%2F3&prefill_Pools-Rounds%20per%20Game=2%2F3&prefill_Region%20Includes=&prefill_%24-Pot%20Split%20Further=,https://airtable.com/appoPE7HV0OWnwLKx/shr1DbTHSjmb6vuSQ?prefill_Tournament=ABEW%20-%20ALL%20-%20%28PC-Fightcade%202%29&prefill_Game=ABEW&prefill_Regions=Global&prefill_Info-Platform=PC-Fightcade%202&prefill_Parent%20Record%20ID=recMYPz2nuadVGJfK&hide_Parent%20Record%20ID=true&prefill_Info-Comments=&prefill_Staff-Commentators=HotdogBongwater420%2CViviMayoi&prefill_Staff-Streame