True,2/3,recUkRhBVSrkmDTCg,70/20/10,32,2024-11-02T19:00:00.000Z,True,recLpkyXao1qR7Mya,"Format notes: If we have a very low number of entrants, I'd switch the format to a round robin with the two best performing players duking it out in a finals match (FT3/Bo5). The winner of such a match would be the #1 ranked player, the loser #2 - the rest of the players would be ranked normally in accordance to the round robin format. Just specifying for the purposes of pot distribution (which in such a case would be mostly from matcherino codes I suppose).",recryC11MNCdo3PC1,9pm,3 Hours,recix3PSFYJmulQLR,3,11/02/2024 9:00 PM,rec5ApUABXyv3gHpe,"Sat. 10/12, Sun. 10/13, Sat. 10/19, Sun. 11/03, Sun. 11/10, Sun. 10/20",Double Elimination,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-online-2024-1/event/change-air-blade-global,0,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/117236,Sat. 11/02,True,2024-11-02T05:00:00.000Z,recix3PSFYJmulQLR,1,2/3,Full Tourney,https://www.twitch.tv/sailorvick,,CET,Sat. 11/09,CAB,ALL,ALL,CAB - ALL - (PC-Fightcade 2),CAB%20-%20ALL%20-%20%28PC-Fightcade%202%29,SailorVick,SonofTzeentch9,SonofTzeentch9,PC-Fightcade,2024-07-03T23:37:38.000Z,Change Air Blade,0%,1,2024-09-11T08:14:40.000Z,recoH5pARDPh5mpf1,Change Air Blade,Manolito_Gallegos#904066,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/117236/admin/general,@SonofTzeentch9,0,,https://www.start.gg/tournament/vortex-gallery-online-2024-1/event/change-air-blade-global,,https://vortexgallery.moe/info#CAB,0,0,0,3,None,a9d00a88,0,0 Hours,FC2,ALL,TheSailorVick,PST,-8,-8,2024-11-02T19:00:00.000Z,2024-11-02T19:00:00.000Z,Global,2024-11-02T20:00:00.000Z,2024-11-02T13:00:00.000Z,11/02 (Sat),11/02 (Sat),11/02 (Sat),2024-11-02T16:00:00.000Z,2024-11-03T00:00:00.000Z,2024-11-02T21:00:00.000Z,11/02 (Sat),2024-11-02T17:00:00.000Z,11/02 (Sat),2024-11-03T04:00:00.000Z,11/03 (Sun),1730577600,Son of Tzeentch 9#3290,Change Air Blade,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/32/32/1726063200000/lkFoA18V7ZQ67XxW7lZyow/YufqugdFIr2ZW1r9OucPK0HXe1lX-44ns