ommunity cheatset and memory card downloaded and setup. The community cheat set can be found in the GBA2 discord. To enable them, launch GBA2, open the cheats menu, and select the option to open a cheat table. Select the GBA2 cheat table and enable ONLY 60FPS and hidden suits. All players should have a 100% memory card in their files, if they need one they can also find it in the GBA2 discord.",Pilot portraits off.,"Epyon, Dark, and Psyco Gundam are banned. We will be using the community cheat set to run the game at 60FPS and make The O, Qubeley, Zeta, and Hamma Hamma selectable.",,,,,,,,,,
