2. Patch the game using the patcher, Six-Patches-of-Pain.
or
1. Acquire it from TO 
Dolphin 5.0-20186 | Link will be provided","90 second time limit.
Damage setting 2
Dog and Karasu are banned.","At the beginning of any set, either player can request a blind pick for character select. The TO can run the blind pick, or assign someone to do this task if the TO is occupied

When beginning a set game 1 stage selection could be either random. Or if you and your opponent can agree on a game 1 stage selection you may go to that desired stage. if you and your opponent can not agree you go random

Winner keeps current character

Loser picks stage or character, not both; if loser picks character, stage returns to neutral

